  "body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en-US\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>ERDDAP - * The List of All Active Datasets in this ERDDAP * - Data Access Form</title>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/erddap/favicon.ico\">\n<link href=\"/erddap/images/erddap2.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" \n  href=\"https://erddap.dataexplorer.oceanobservatories.org/erddap/rss/allDatasets.rss\" \n  title=\"ERDDAP: * The List of All Active Datasets in this ERDDAP *\">\n\n</head>\n<body> <table class=\"compact nowrap\" style=\"width:100%; background-color:#013869;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"text-align:center; width:80px;\"><a rel=\"bookmark\"\n      href=\"https://oceanobservatories.org/\"><img\n      title=\"OOI\"\n      src=\"/erddap/images/ooi_banner.jpg\" alt=\"OOI\"\n      style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"></a></td>\n    <td style=\"text-align:right; font-size:small; padding-right: 10px;\">\n      <br/><br/><br/>\n      <span style=\"color:#ddd\">\n      <a title=\"NSF\" href=\"https://www.nsf.gov/\" style=\"color: #ccc;\">\n      Brought to you by NSF</a></span>\n      </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<!-- Big HTML tooltips are generated with wz_tooltip from \n    http://wztip.info/index.php/Main_Page (LGPL license) -->\n<script src=\"http://erddap.dataexplorer.oceanobservatories.org/erddap/images/wz_tooltip.js\"></script>\n\n<!-- Drag and Drop is performed by wz_dragdrop from\n     http://www.walterzorn.com/dragdrop/dragdrop_e.htm (LGPL license) -->\n<script src=\"http&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;erddap&#x2e;dataexplorer&#x2e;oceanobservatories&#x2e;org&#x2f;erddap&#x2f;images&#x2f;wz_dragdrop.js\"></script>\n\n<div class=\"standard_width\">\n\n<h1 class=\"nowrap\"><a title=\"Click here to return to the ERDDAP home page.\" \nrel=\"start\" href=\"http://erddap.dataexplorer.oceanobservatories.org/erddap/index.html\">ERDDAP</a>\n &gt; <a rel=\"contents\" href=\"http&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;erddap&#x2e;dataexplorer&#x2e;oceanobservatories&#x2e;org&#x2f;erddap&#x2f;tabledap&#x2f;index&#x2e;html&#x3f;page&#x3d;1&#x26;itemsPerPage&#x3d;1000\">tabledap</a>\n &gt; Data Access Form\n<img src=\"http&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;erddap&#x2e;dataexplorer&#x2e;oceanobservatories&#x2e;org&#x2f;erddap&#x2f;images&#x2f;QuestionMark&#x2e;png\" alt=\"&#x3f;\" onmouseover=\"Tip('<div class=&quot;standard_max_width&quot;>This Data Access Form helps you download a subset of the data from a dataset with <strong>tabular data</strong> via the OPeNDAP protocol. In tabular datasets, the dataset is represented as a table with columns and rows. Each column (a variable) has one type of data (e.g., Sea Surface Temperature). Each row represents a different sample of the data (e.g., from a different time or location).<p><strong>To download tabular data:</strong> <ol> <li>Select (check) the variables you want to download. <li>Specify constraints for any of the variables (not just the selected variables) to get the subset of data that you want. In most cases, you will at least specify longitude and latitude, or time constraints. <li>For <kbd>File type</kbd>, choose one of the non-image file types (anything but .kml, .pdf, or .png).</ol> This web page just simplifies the creation of tabledap URLs. <br><strong>If you want, you can create these URLs by hand or have a computer program do it.</strong> <br>Then you don\\&#39;t have to use this form to get data. See the \\&#39;Bypass this form\\&#39; link below.</div>')\" onmouseout=\"UnTip()\"  >\n\n</h1>\n<table class=\"compact nowrap\">\n  <tr>\n    <td>Dataset Title:&nbsp;</td>\n    <td style=\"vertical-align:middle\"><span class=\"standoutColor\" style=\"font-size:130%; line-height:130%;\"><strong>* The List of All Active Datasets in this ERDDAP *</strong>\n      <a rel=\"alternate\" \n  href=\"https://erddap.dataexplorer.oceanobservatories.org/erddap/subscriptions/add.html?datasetID=allDatasets&amp;showErrors=false&amp;email=\" \n  title=\"\"><img alt=\"Subscribe\"\n    title=\"Get&#x20;an&#x20;email&#x20;immediately&#x20;whenever&#x20;this&#x20;dataset&#x20;changes&#x2e;&#x2e;&#x2e;\" \n    src=\"http://erddap.dataexplorer.oceanobservatories.org/erddap/images/e",
